---
title: One-Sheet Sausage and Pepper Hoagies with Broiled Asparagus
description: This ballpark classic is perfect for baseball season! All the components are cooked on the same baking sheet, leaving you with almost no cleanup. That way, you’ll be able to sit back and enjoy the game.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-sheet-sausage-and-pepper-hoagies-c94e3bda.jpg
